data.description: Single family energy efficient home sits on a premium lot including a full cul-de-sac, a backyard with a view, vaulted ceilings, open floor plan, LOTS OF natural LIGHT & upgrades: spacious foyer, large formal dining room, family room & enclosed sun room. A gourmet kitchen w/granite counters, white cabinetry, a bar, eat-in kitchen area & stainless-steel appliances. First Floor Primary bedroom with walk-in closet & bathroom with marble counters. All baths have MARBLE!! Second floor has 1 bedroom, 1 full bath and a LOFT that would be fabulous for an office. MORE UPGRADES:  Custom wood window treatments & blinds; luxury plank floors; extended patio; upgraded epoxy garage floors; custom remote blinds & HUGE FLOORED walk-in storage!  *Premier Adult 55+ community; however, 20% of homeowners can be under 55.  No one under 18.  Amenities include indoor/outdoor pool, park w/gazebo, additional park, community activities, billiards, exercise room, seasonal parties and so MUCH more! Pet friendly.
